h3. Summary
Based on our [Confluence REST API documentation|https://docs.atlassian.com/atlassian-confluence/REST/latest/], to get a piece of information of a content by using [this REST call function|https://docs.atlassian.com/atlassian-confluence/REST/latest/#d3e136], there are request query parameters that can be used;_status_, _version_ and _expand_.
